<br>
Serenity:good for leveling but post level 50 fights last on the order of say 30 seconds on average serentiy in RvR seems wasted when you regen all your power back on the portal pad.<br>
<br>
So what else can you really do to effect your battlesongs with realm skills your class defining attribute and its very lacking with ways to customize its skills. Perhaps add chance to critical hit for all speed classes instant DD(Access to Wild Power). Doesn't seem overpowering considering the low base dmg. <br>
